  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770570/extras/31cec4a56471cc33c57e662f2a92c972.webp?t=1770723531\" width=616 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Biscudo</strong> is a classic strategic grid-based game where every move counts! Challenge your opponents in a battle of wits as you compete to claim the most squares by strategically drawing edges. With simple mechanics yet deep tactical gameplay, Biscudo offers an engaging experience for players of all skill levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770570/extras/dbcb1d9ed0d704bb4a3d29ac363b7973.webp?t=1770723531\" width=616 height=61 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take turns</strong> drawing unclaimed edges on the board.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete a square</strong> by drawing its last remaining edge to claim it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Powerups!</strong> Special squares to spice up the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chain your moves </strong>— if you complete two squares at once, you earn an extra turn!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Outsmart your opponent</strong> by setting up combos while avoiding giving them easy claims.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Win the game</strong> by claiming the most squares when the board is full.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770570/extras/48fcff225bf645e0b9eaa0a8b50acc54.webp?t=1770723531\" width=616 height=61 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ Compete against Bots or challenge a friend in a local match or online <br>✔ Clean, intuitive visuals for a seamless experience<br>✔ Perfect for quick matches or deep strategic play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to dominate the board?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770570/extras/31cec4a56471cc33c57e662f2a92c972.webp?t=1770723531\" width=616 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Biscudo</strong> is a classic strategic grid-based game where every move counts! Challenge your opponents in a battle of wits as you compete to claim the most squares by strategically drawing edges. With simple mechanics yet deep tactical gameplay, Biscudo offers an engaging experience for players of all skill levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770570/extras/dbcb1d9ed0d704bb4a3d29ac363b7973.webp?t=1770723531\" width=616 height=61 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take turns</strong> drawing unclaimed edges on the board.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete a square</strong> by drawing its last remaining edge to claim it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Powerups!</strong> Special squares to spice up the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chain your moves </strong>— if you complete two squares at once, you earn an extra turn!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Outsmart your opponent</strong> by setting up combos while avoiding giving them easy claims.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Win the game</strong> by claiming the most squares when the board is full.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770570/extras/48fcff225bf645e0b9eaa0a8b50acc54.webp?t=1770723531\" width=616 height=61 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔ Compete against Bots or challenge a friend in a local match or online <br>✔ Clean, intuitive visuals for a seamless experience<br>✔ Perfect for quick matches or deep strategic play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to dominate the board?</p>",
